---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Home" description="Learn to deliver real projects by directing AI.">
  <Hero
    heading="Build real software. Direct AI to do it."
    subtitle="Learn to deliver real projects by directing AI."
    ctaText="Start here"
    ctaHref="/getting-started"
  />

  <!-- Categories -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <h2 class="mb-2">Six disciplines. One methodology.</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">Each category has six projects that take you from beginner to production-grade. The same loop — plan, build, verify, deploy, reflect — applied to different domains.</p>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <Card title="Web Development" metadata="Available" href="/web-dev">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build full-stack web apps, APIs, and deployed systems. Static sites to production-grade multi-user platforms.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-success bg-success-bg px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">6 projects ready</span></p>
      </Card>
      <Card title="Data Engineering">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build data pipelines, warehouses, and dashboards. Raw data to automated reporting.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-text-muted bg-bg-muted px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Coming soon</span></p>
      </Card>
      <Card title="Machine Learning">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build ML models, training pipelines, and prediction APIs. Datasets to deployed models.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-text-muted bg-bg-muted px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Coming soon</span></p>
      </Card>
      <Card title="AI Integration">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build apps powered by language models, embeddings, and AI agents. Prompts to production systems.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-text-muted bg-bg-muted px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Coming soon</span></p>
      </Card>
      <Card title="Cybersecurity">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build secure systems, audit tools, and incident response playbooks. Vulnerabilities to hardened infrastructure.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-text-muted bg-bg-muted px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Coming soon</span></p>
      </Card>
      <Card title="Cloud & DevOps">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">Build cloud infrastructure, CI/CD pipelines, and container orchestration. Local to scalable deployments.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-text-muted bg-bg-muted px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Coming soon</span></p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <h2 class="mb-2">How it works</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">You direct. AI builds. You verify.</p>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-5">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Plan</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Give AI a brief and a template. Catch scope creep before any code is written.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Build</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Direct AI through tickets. Branch, implement, test, review, merge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Verify</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Open the product and test it like a real user. Try to break it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">4</div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Deploy</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Ship to a real URL. Verify it works in production, not just on your laptop.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">5</div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Reflect</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">What went well? What did AI get wrong? What acceptance criteria were missing?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-6">The loop gets faster each time because you've done it before.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Who This Is For -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <h2 class="mb-6">Who this is for</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">University students</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Who need to build technical outputs — apps, dashboards, pipelines — across degrees that aren't computer science.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Self-taught learners</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Who want to build real things but don't know where to start with the tooling, the process, or the deployment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Career changers</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Who need a portfolio of working, deployed projects and a methodology they can describe in interviews.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes This Different -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <h2 class="mb-6">What makes this different</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary"><strong class="text-text">You direct AI to write the code</strong> — and learn to read, inspect, and challenge it. The skill transfers to any tech stack, any domain, any tool.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary"><strong class="text-text">Real projects, not exercises.</strong> You deploy to real URLs, integrate real payment systems, and handle real edge cases.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary"><strong class="text-text">Six projects, increasing complexity.</strong> Each project adds a new capability and a new directing challenge you won't find in tutorials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary"><strong class="text-text">Free and open.</strong> No subscription. No paywall.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Need -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <h2 class="mb-6">What you need</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">A computer (Mac, Windows, or Linux)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">A Claude Pro or Max subscription (~$20/month — this is how you access Claude Code)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">About 30–60 minutes for initial setup</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">No programming experience required</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>


  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pb-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to start?</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-6">Read how it works, install the tools, and build your first project.</p>
    <a
      href="/getting-started"
      class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-md transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg"
    >
      Start here
    </a>
  </section>
</LandingLayout>
